      "type": "trident-feature-block",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Power & Range",
        "body": "Choose between a cadence sensor for relaxed cruising or a torque sensor for a natural ride feel. The 48V 17.5Ah Samsung-cell battery delivers up to 80km of pedal-assisted range.",
